) AS [t]

    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ApplicationUserId], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[Count], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[DataStatus], [s].[Description], [s].[Gender], [s].[Model], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[Size], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [i].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus0], [i].[ImageLocalPath], [i].[ImageUrl], [i].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate0], [i].[ShoeId], [t1].[ShoeId] AS [ShoeId0], [t1].[HashtagId], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus1], [t1].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate1], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DataStatus0] AS [DataStatus00], [t1].[ModifiedDate0] AS [ModifiedDate00], [t1].[Text]

    LEFT JOIN (

        FROM [ShoeHashtags] AS [s0]
        INNER JOIN [Hashtags] AS [h] ON [s0].[HashtagId] = [h].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[ShoeId]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ApplicationUserId], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[Count], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[DataStatus], [s].[Description], [s].[Gender], [s].[Model], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[Size], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [i].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus0], [i].[ImageLocalPath], [i].[ImageUrl], [i].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate0], [i].[ShoeId], [t1].[ShoeId] AS [ShoeId0], [t1].[HashtagId], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus1], [t1].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate1], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DataStatus0] AS [DataStatus00], [t1].[ModifiedDate0] AS [ModifiedDate00], [t1].[Text]

        INNER JOIN [Hashtags] AS [h] ON [s0].[HashtagId] = [h].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Balance], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[ProfileImageLocalPath], [a].[ProfileImageUrl], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[UserName] = @__username_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[ApplicationUserId], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[Count], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[DataStatus], [s].[Description], [s].[Gender], [s].[Model], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[Size], [i].[Id] AS [Id0], [i].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [i].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus0], [i].[ImageLocalPath], [i].[ImageUrl], [i].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate0], [i].[ShoeId], [t1].[ShoeId] AS [ShoeId0], [t1].[HashtagId], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus1], [t1].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate1], [t1].[Id] AS [Id1], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DataStatus0] AS [DataStatus00], [t1].[ModifiedDate0] AS [ModifiedDate00], [t1].[Text]
    FROM [Shoes] AS [s]
    LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [s].[Id] = [i].[ShoeId]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [s0].[ShoeId], [s0].[HashtagId], [s0].[CreatedDate], [s0].[DataStatus], [s0].[ModifiedDate], [h].[Id], [h].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [h].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus0], [h].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate0], [h].[Text]
        FROM [ShoeHashtags] AS [s0]
        INNER JOIN [Hashtags] AS [h] ON [s0].[HashtagId] = [h].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [s].[Id] = [t1].[ShoeId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ApplicationUserId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ShoeId0], [t0].[HashtagId]

    WHERE [h].[Text] = @__hashtag_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[ShoeId], [s].[HashtagId], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[DataStatus], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s0].[Id], [s0].[ApplicationUserId], [s0].[Brand], [s0].[CategoryId], [s0].[Color], [s0].[Count], [s0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [s0].[DataStatus] AS [DataStatus0], [s0].[Description], [s0].[Gender], [s0].[Model], [s0].[ModifiedDate] AS [ModifiedDate0], [s0].[Size]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[Balance], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[ProfileImageLocalPath], [a].[ProfileImageUrl], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[ApplicationUserId], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[DataStatus], [c].[ItemsCount], [c].[ModifiedDate], [c].[TotalPrice]
